data.description: This 4 bed, 2 bath northwest home is situated on a cul-de-sac lot in the desirable Bluffs community. With parks, schools, golf courses, and shopping nearby, ensuring convenience and leisure at your fingertips. Step inside to discover a freshly painted home, spacious kitchen with a brand new hardware and backsplash, seamlessly blending into a grand great room, all beneath soaring high ceilings. For those who appreciate formal dining, a dining area is also at your disposal. Beyond the interior, a full-length covered patio awaits adorned with a sparkling pool, meticulously manicured landscaping and a lush grassy area. This property embodies the perfect blend of comfort and outdoor entertainment.
